r bright finish and to remove light "metal fuzz" or lap lines without disturbing the essential dimensions of the work.</p>        </div><!--col-left-->                <div class="col-right">        <?php include_once ('includes/r-buffingcompounds.php'); ?>        <?php include_once ('includes/hp-right.php'); ?>	        </div><!--col-right--><?php include_once ('includes/footer.php'); ?>        